# ROOT CAUSE FIX: Comprehensive .gitignore for EDA/Verification Projects
# 
# ISSUE: Commit 191cbe1 added 200+ simulation build artifacts to git
# CAUSE: Inadequate .gitignore allowed csrc/, simv.daidir/, logs, etc. to be tracked
# EFFECT: Every simulation run creates new files with different process IDs -> unlimited growth
#
# This comprehensive .gitignore prevents tracking build artifacts that cause storage bloat

# =============================================================================
# SIMULATION ARTIFACTS (Primary cause of unlimited storage growth)
# =============================================================================

# VCS/Synopsys Simulator
simv*
csrc/
simv.daidir/
ucli.key
inter.vpd
DVEfiles/
worklib/

# Questa/ModelSim
