# =============================================================================
# NOTES FOR DEVELOPERS
# =============================================================================
#
# To clean up already-tracked files:
# 1. git rm -r --cached 9x9_vip/*/sim/csrc/
# 2. git rm -r --cached 9x9_vip/*/sim/simv.daidir/
# 3. git rm -r --cached 9x9_vip/*/sim/verdiLog/
# 4. git rm --cached 9x9_vip/*/sim/*.fsdb
# 5. git rm --cached 9x9_vip/*/sim/*.log
# 6. git commit -m "Remove simulation artifacts from git tracking"
#
# This will prevent the unlimited storage growth issue.
#